title: more docs
body: Not clear from the README what is the core difference from TreeExp, support of Chip-Seq data? I am currently doing multi-species comparisons of gene expressions and I want to understand what are the optimal packages

title: Exporting standard file format
body: Hi! Is there any way to export trees in a standard file format? Something like the Newick tree file format (`.treefile` as described here: https://evolution.genetics.washington.edu/phylip/newicktree.html)
